Name: AccountDescriptiveName
Notes: The descriptive name of the Customer account.

Name: AdFormat
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
TEXT / text
IMAGE / image
DYNAMIC_IMAGE / dynamic_image
FLASH / flash
VIDEO / video
HTML / html
AUDIO / audio
COMPOSITE / composite
PRINT / print
Notes: The underlying media format of the ad. Values can be one of the formats on the Template Ads page, or a MediaType enum.

Name: AdGroupStatus
Enum Values:

ENABLED / enabled
PAUSED / paused
REMOVED / removed

Name: AdNetworkType2
Enum Values:

Name: AoiMostSpecificTargetId
Display Name: Most specific location target (Location of interest)
Notes: The most specific location target (Location of interest).

Name: CampaignLocationTargetId
Notes: Location ID of the matching campaign criterion.

Name: CampaignStatus
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
ENABLED / enabled
PAUSED / paused
REMOVED / removed

Name: CityCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the city Location associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: ClickType
Enum Values:
URL_CLICKS / Headline
CALLS / Phone calls
OTHER / Other
PRODUCT_EXTENSION_CLICKS / Product plusbox offer
SITELINKS / Sitelink
PRODUCT_LISTING_AD_CLICKS / Shopping ad - Standard
GET_DIRECTIONS / Driving direction
OFFER_PRINTS / Print offer
BREADCRUMBS / Breadcrumbs
CALL_TRACKING / Manually dialed phone calls
MOBILE_CALL_TRACKING / Mobile phone calls
LOCATION_EXPANSION / Get location details
VIDEO_WEBSITE_CLICKS / Website
VIDEO_CALL_TO_ACTION_CLICKS / Call-to-Action overlay
VIDEO_APP_STORE_CLICKS / App store
VIDEO_CARD_ACTION_HEADLINE_CLICKS / Cards
VIDEO_END_CAP_CLICKS / End cap
CLICK_ON_ENGAGEMENT_AD / Click on engagement ad
UNKNOWN / unknown
Notes: The Impressions field will reflect how often the ad was served with that click type available. Since ads can serve with multiple click types displayed, impressions may be double counted and the totals may not be accurate.

Name: CountryCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the country Location associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: Device
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / Other
DESKTOP / Computers
HIGH_END_MOBILE / Mobile devices with full browsers
TABLET / Tablets with full browsers
Notes: Device type where the impression was shown.

Name: LopMostSpecificTargetId
Notes: The most specific location target (Physical location).

Name: MetroCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the metro area Location associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: MonthOfYear
Enum Values:
JANUARY / January
FEBRUARY / February
MARCH / March
APRIL / April
MAY / May
JUNE / June
JULY / July

Notes: The name of the month of the year, e.g., "December".

Name: Page
Notes: Page number in search results where the ad was shown.

Name: RegionCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the region Location associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.
